===Etymology===
From {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|ἐπιστήμη||science, knowledge|tr=epistēmē|lang=grc|sc=polytonic}}, from {{term|ἐπίσταμαι||I know|tr=epistamai|lang=grc|sc=polytonic}} + {{term|-λογία||discourse|tr=logia|lang=grc|sc=polytonic}}, from {{term|λέγω||I speak|tr=legō|lang=grc|sc=polytonic}}. The term was introduced into English by the Scottish philosopher James Frederick Ferrier (1808-1864).

